    "title": "Belly Button Biodiversity Dashboard",
    "description": "Use JavaScript, CSS, D3, Plotly to build interactive dashboard",
    "html": "<h1 class=\"my-4\">Belly Button Biodiversity Dashboard</h1>\n\n    <ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <li class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n        <a href=\"/portfolio-1-col\">Portfolio</a>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">JS CSS D3</li>\n    </ol>\n    <p>Use JavaScript, CSS, D3, Plotly to build interactive dashboard</p>\n    <hr>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-2\">\n        <div class=\"well\">\n          <h5>Test Subject ID:</h5>\n          <select id=\"selDataset\" onchange=\"optionChanged(this.value)\"></select>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"panel panel-primary\">\n          <div class=\"panel-heading\">\n            <h3 class=\"panel-title\">Demographic Info</h3>\n          </div>\n          <div id=\"sample-metadata\" class=\"panel-body\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n        <div id=\"bar\"></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n        <div id=\"gauge\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <div id=\"bubble\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>"
